            "body": "`queries/**/*.scm` are recognized as query files, with their own ftplugin -- which sets a different `iskeyword`, including `!` (inherited from Lisp, which this is a dialect of).\r\n\r\nThis makes `!` illegal; you can test with other Lisp files.",
